msgid "Device access"
msgstr "设备访问"

#: ../../sandbox-permissions.rst:108
msgid ""
"While not ideal, ``--device=all`` can be used to access devices like "
"controllers or webcams."
msgstr "尽管不理想， `` --device=all ``  可以用来访问控制器和网络摄像头之类的设备。"

